  • Constructor Details

    • Appointment

      public Appointment(int appointmentID, int customerID, int userID, int contactID, String title, String description, String location, String type, LocalDateTime start, LocalDateTime end, LocalDateTime createDate, String createdBy, LocalDateTime lastUpdate, String lastUpdateBy)
      Constructor for creating Appointment objects.
      Parameters:
      appointmentID - int for tracking unique ID per appointment.
      contactID - int for tracking unique Contact object associated with an appointment.
      userID - int for tracking unique User object associated with an appointment.
      customerID - int for tracking unique Customer object associated with an appointment.
      title - String value for naming appointments.
      description - String value for giving a short description of an appointment.
      location - String value for declaring where an appointment takes place.
      type - String value for assigning a type to an appointment.
      start - LocalDateTime for tracking when an appointment starts.
      end - LocalDate time for tracking when an appointment ends.
      createDate - LocalDateTime for tracking when an appointment was created.
      createdBy - String for tracking who (usually a username) that created the appointment.
      lastUpdate - LocalDateTime for tracking when an appointment was last updated.
      lastUpdateBy - String for tracking who (usually a username) last updated the appointment.

    • Appointment

      Empty constructor for creating a new blank appointment.
